<Content>Best New Years Ever at Damai I don't usually write reviews on tripadvisor, but I felt such an obligation to after visiting Damai. We were there for three nights during our honeymoon. We stayed at four places on the island (including the Four Seasons Jimbaran) and this was by FAR our most favorite place. The intimacy, simple luxury, and attention to detail is unsurpassed. We absolutely LOVED our room, the food and the company. We spent New Years Eve at Damai and had an amazing 8 course meal with new friends we met there. I won't go on and on about the food, since everyone does, but it is really amazing. We live in the city of Chicago and are big foodies-this was some of the best food we have ever eaten. We really enjoyed getting to know the manager and his fiancee and loved the feel of the entire place. We had big plans to do things all around the North end of the island, but once we got settled at Damai we never wanted to leave. It is a truly magical and romantic place. If you have the chance to go, DO IT! 
