<Content>Beautiful resort What a beautiful resort... We spent 5 nights here in June 2005 and had an excellent stay. The staff is extremely friendly and will go out of their way to make sure you are pleased. There were so many small things that together with the beautiful surroundings made our vacation complete. The staff would bring mosquito repellant to the private balconys in the evening, a print of today's menu was put in the rooms during the day, etc. When lying in our private jacuzzi at night, looking at the sky bright with stars, you just don't want to leave this gem... The food was really great and the rooms are fantastic - and since every room is an independant house you are not disturbed by noise from the room next door. Amazing view from the pool. The girls in the outdoor spa are so kind and give great massages. The spa is a bit rustic and the girls' English skills are not the best but this is way compensated by their friendly and warm personalities. I can absolutely recommend this wonderful resort - especially if you want to go somewhere peaceful and romantic. 
