<Content>Incredible beauty and serenity The Damai is an exceptional experience 鈥?we strongly recommend both this particular property and Bali in general. After a wonderful five night stay at the Uma in Ubud, we were picked up by a very professional and friendly Damai driver and spent three outstanding nights at the hotel. We chose the Damai on account of the praise it has received in this and other forums; we were not disappointed. The setting is picturesque and intimate, the staff is highly skilled, and the food is extraordinary. The garden baths with outdoor tubs and showers are especially nice. The hotel manager, Glenn, has done an amazing job utilizing organic and conscientious self-sustaining methods, while at the same time maintaining a magnificent level of comfort and quality. Although he is very discreet and low-key, we observed his evident love for the Balinese culture and people, and we were happy to support a business that cares about the local community. This is a hotel where one can find peace and witness the beauty of Balinese village life. - Jim and Kris, Seattle 
